## 🔗 Step 3: Flutter ↔ iOS 연결

### 3-1. Method Channel 업데이트

**파일:** `ios/Runner/AppDelegate.swift`

**확인 사항:**
```swift
// Method channel이 제대로 연결되어 있는지 확인
let channel = FlutterMethodChannel(name: "com.yourapp.rememo/analyzer", ...)

channel.setMethodCallHandler({ [weak self] (call: FlutterMethodCall, result: @escaping FlutterResult) in
    if call.method == "analyzeScreenshot" {
        // ContentAnalyzerAdapter 호출
        let adapter = ContentAnalyzerAdapter.shared
        let analysisResult = await adapter.analyze(textBlocks: ..., imageSize: ...)
        result(analysisResult)
    }
})
```

---

### 3-2. Flutter에서 호출

**파일:** `lib/services/analyzer_service.dart`

```dart
class AnalyzerService {
  static const platform = MethodChannel('com.yourapp.rememo/analyzer');
  
  Future<MemoModel> analyzeScreenshot(String imagePath) async {
    try {
      final result = await platform.invokeMethod('analyzeScreenshot', {
        'imagePath': imagePath,
      });
      
      return MemoModel.fromJson(result as Map<String, dynamic>);
    } catch (e) {
      print('Error: $e');
      rethrow;
    }
  }
}
```

